    "type": "message",
    "text": "I am really into Observable. I am not sure that it's obvious that it is a streaming FRP implementation. I starting writing up some of the more intricate ways you can compute with its streams\n\n<https://observablehq.com/@tomlarkworthy/switch-dataflow>\n\nI think it's amazing that there is a decent FRP programmable IDE out now.",
